			I am a High Elf Enchanter from Felwithe. I am not an expert on this spell, but I know that caution must be utilized when practicing it.  I recently acquired ALLIANCE and cast it on a pixie trickster to see what it might do to improve my faction with them, since I had killed so many of them in the past.  It made the pixie &quot;appear more friendly&quot;.  Fine, I thought, until I reached my guild for my practices and was rudely awakened to find that the spell was still in effect and I was &quot;Charming&quot; the trainer.  He did not appreciate that and swiftly slain me.  I was Killed in my own Guild, very embarrassing.  My mastering of this spell will continue, but I do believe I might end up loosing my life once again in the process.  So, my word of advice, test close to your where you are bound.  
